[Nouns] vaporization, volatilization; gasification, evaporation, vaporation; distillation, cupellation, cohabilition, sublimination, exhalation; volatility.
vaporizer, still, retort; fumigation, steraming; bay salt, chloride of sodium.
[Verbs] render gaseous [more]; vaporize, volatilize; distill, sublime; evaporate, exhale, smoke, transpire, emit vapor, fume, reek, steam, fumigate; cohobate; finestill.
[Adjectives] volatilized; reeking; volatile; evaporable, vaporizable.
